item.content:encoded: [trx_section background="#5ea281" padding="30px 0 60px 0"] [trx_content] [trx_icon icon="icon-down-open" size="20" color="#fff" box_style="circle" align="center" style="border: 3px solid #fff;" bg_color="transparent" bottom="60"] [trx_title type="2" color="#fff" align="center" bottom="20"]Who we are[/trx_title] [trx_title type="6" color="#fff" align="center" bottom="60"]Professional team of ThemeRex studio presents this terrific Infographic Theme[/trx_title] [trx_points type="1" top="30" bottom="60"] [trx_point_item icon=" icon-camera67" color="#5ea281" background="#f6f6ea" link="#"]Fully Customizable[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item icon="icon-human50" color="#5ea281" background="#f6f6ea" link="#"]About Studio[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item icon="icon-left36" color="#5ea281" background="#f6f6ea" link="#"]Project Team[/trx_point_item] [/trx_points] [trx_more id="tab_1s"] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section id="tab_1s" background="#eff0ea"] [trx_content] [trx_tabs style="3" initial="1" tab_names="Fully Customizable|About Studio|Project Team"] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center"]FULLY Customizable[/trx_title] [trx_text size="16" align="center" bottom="60"]RockGroup is an Infographic theme that offers infinite options for creation of the unique layout for your website.[/trx_text] [trx_slider engine="swiper" pagination="no" count="3" controls="yes" titles="no" height="455" width="950" left="auto" right="auto" bottom="30"] [trx_slider_item src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/2342.png"] [trx_slider_item src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5645.png"] [trx_slider_item src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7686.png"] [/trx_slider] [trx_text size="16" align="center"]We created three popular infographic skins for business, ecology and politics. You may use these templates both for these themes and for many others, since they are quite versatile.[/trx_text] [/trx_tab] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center" bottom="60"]About STUDIO[/trx_title] [trx_columns columns="12" bottom="30"] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv1.png" url="none" width="44"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]With Love to Customers[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]ThemeRex is a studio that aims to make their user’s experience easier and much more pleasant. You probalby won’t have a better opportunity to make sure of their competence, as well as friendliness towards their customers. Vast experience and understanding of each product’s peculiarities let ThemeRex create outstanding business solutions. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv2.png" url="none" width="42"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]High Professionalism[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]Many year experience and hundreds of successful projects have made ThemeRex a professional on the web area. Within this period of time, the company has gone through a serious evolution from amateurs to leaders. We create templates for your websites that will increase your reputation and highlight your professionalism and leadership. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [/trx_columns] [trx_columns columns="12"] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv3.png" url="none" width="42"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]Serving Clients’ Goals[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]ThemeRex is doing their best to grant each owner of their themes with maximum opportunities to present their individuality, show their achievements, and establish the best contact with their audience. Using their rich experience, world’s innovations and their own web solutions the ThemeRex team creates templates that will solve your business’s tasks at maximum degree. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv4.png" url="none" width="34"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]Reliability and Prestige[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]Purchasing products from ThemeRex means entrusting your reputation to one of the best web-studios. ThemeRex company does its work with its customer in mind. That is why you are getting the best product that will perfectly suit your needs. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [/trx_columns] [/trx_tab] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center" bottom="60"]Project Team[/trx_title] [trx_team indent="yes" rounding="yes" style="3" columns="4"] [trx_team_item user="trx_user" name="Margarita Andrews" position="Web Designer" photo="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/bird_1-e1418313445363.png"] [/trx_team_item] [trx_team_item user="trx_user" name="Rosemarie Russell" align="left" position="Web Developer" photo="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/bird_2-e1418313479211.png"] [/trx_team_item] [trx_team_item user="trx_user" name="Leonard Gregory" position="Project Manager" photo="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/bird_3-e1418313510938.png"] [/trx_team_item] [/trx_team] [/trx_tab] [/trx_tabs] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#a7d692" padding="90px 0 0 0"] [trx_content] [trx_text size="90" color="#fff" weight="700" align="center" height="90" bottom="30"]6231[/trx_text] [trx_text size="24" color="#fff" weight="300" align="center" height="35" bottom="60"]...cups of coffee was consumed by our team in 2014. And yes, this figure here is for no reason. And we are presenting you TRX SKILLS WIDGET specially stylized for ROCK GROUP[/trx_text] [trx_rocks count="6" maximum="6250" color="#fff" width="700" left="auto" right="auto" bottom="60"] [trx_rocks_item level="5478" title="L1"] [trx_rocks_item level="1056" title="L2"] [trx_rocks_item level="4568" title="L3"] [trx_rocks_item level="3345" title="L4"] [trx_rocks_item level="6231" title="L5"] [trx_rocks_item level="2256" title="L6"] [/trx_rocks] [trx_more id="widget"] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section id="widget" background="#eff0ea" padding="100px 0"] [trx_content width="1100"] [trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/234r.png" url="none" width="432" align="left" right="70"] [trx_block align="left" width="570"] [trx_title type="1" bottom="40"]Skills Widget[/trx_title] [trx_text]To display your knowledge and skills graphically, you have a specially designed widget at your disposal, such as "TRX Skills". You may choose unlimited number of skills, name them, set the level, color and one of the display styles. Vivamus vel mauris id turpis scelerisque ullamcorper. Ut non velit blandit neque aliquam finibus. Donec ornare tortor ac arcu elementum fermentum. Suspendisse rhoncus est vitae leo rutrum congue. Pellentesque nisl sapien, mollis sit amet eros in, imperdiet tempus tortor. Nulla eu lobortis sem. Mauris vitae aliquet tortor. [/trx_text] [trx_button skin="global" style="regular" size="big" top="10"]Read More[/trx_button] [/trx_block] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fcfcf7" padding="90px 0 30px 0"] [trx_content] [trx_title type="2" align="center" height="35" bottom="30"]Rock Group is easily adaptable to any mobile device[/trx_title] [trx_text color="#8b8b8b" align="center" size="24" weight="300" height="35" bottom="60"]The fact of prevalence of mobile devices obliges to adjust any website to peculiarities of their screens at max. We have done our best for your website based on Rock Group to blend with this trend.[/trx_text] [trx_points type="2" arrows="yes"] [trx_point_item image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/ledcinema.png" background="#d7d6cb"]RETINA READY[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/macbook.png" background="#d7d6cb"]TABLET FRIENDLY[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/mobile.png" background="#d7d6cb"]100% RESPONSIVE[/trx_point_item] [/trx_points] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fcfcf7" padding="30px 0"] [trx_line] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fcfcf7" padding="30px 0 90px 0"] [trx_content] [trx_title type="2" align="center" bottom="30"]What we do[/trx_title] [trx_title type="6" align="center" bottom="60"]More information about rock group features[/trx_title] [trx_text size="24" height="35" align="center" weight="300" bottom="60"]ThemeRex worked out an amazing combination of vast fucntionalilty and user’s comfort. Thanks to an amazingly user friendly TRX Framework, customers have a chance to customize their theme the way they like.[/trx_text] [trx_chart width="550" legend="no" title="100%result" bottom="80" align="center"] [trx_chart_item level="25" title="100% Responsive" color="#c0c192" icon="icon-mountains" icon_color="#c0c192"]The fact of prevalence of mobile devices obliges to adjust any actual website to their peculiarity at maximum degree.[/trx_chart_item] [trx_chart_item level="50" title="Free Support" color="#c44b12" icon=" icon-favorite" icon_color="#c44b12"]Our Support Team is ready to become your reliable guide in the World of RockGroup. We provide free access to theme Documentation and our Ticket Sys.[/trx_chart_item] [trx_chart_item level="75" title="Shortcodes" color="#669c75" icon="icon-tribal" icon_color="#669c75"]Rock Group includes the most full set of Shortcodes, amongst which you can find those you can get only in ThemeRex products.[/trx_chart_item] [trx_chart_item level="85" title="SEO Ready" color="#3d9ba9" icon="icon-man" icon_color="#3d9ba9"]HTML5 code integrated into the theme meets the best SEO approaches. The theme supports compatibility with advanced SEO plugins.[/trx_chart_item] [/trx_chart] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#eff0ea" padding="90px 0 0 0"] [trx_content] [trx_title type="2" align="center" bottom="30"]TRX framework[/trx_title] [trx_title type="6" align="center" bottom="90"]COMBINATION OF VAST FUNCTIONALITY AND USER’S COMFORT![/trx_title] [trx_around bottom="-11" image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/7.png" width="900" align="center"] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Unique Setting Inheritance and Override System[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Raiting \ Review Mechanism and Media Content Manager[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Shortcode Builder or Visual Composer[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Unique ThemeRex Shortcodes[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Custom Theme Options Panel[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Advanced Translation Options[/trx_around_item] [/trx_around] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#7DC2CE" padding="60px 0 0 0"] [trx_content] [trx_text align="center" color="#fff" weight="300" height="35" size="24" bottom="30"]Common settings can be overriden for any page/category/post. For instance, you can assign your own set of parameters for each category: color scheme, sidebars, menu type, style of slider and many more.[/trx_text] [trx_more id="video_sd"] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#7DC2CE" padding="0 0 90px 0" id="video_sd"] [trx_content] [trx_video url="http://vimeo.com/69268599" autoplay="off" image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/TiffanyBug.jpg"] [trx_text align="center" color="#fff" weight="300" height="24" size="16"]TRX Framework is a result of accumulated experience of WordPress theme development and constant contact with customers. The team worked out an amazing combination of vast functionality and user’s comfort. Thanks to an incredibly user friendly TRX Framework, customers have a chance to customize their theme the way they like.[/trx_text] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#53acbb"] You may use these templates both for these themes and for many others, since they are quite versatile.[/trx_text] [/trx_tab] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center" bottom="60"]About STUDIO[/trx_title] [trx_columns columns="12" bottom="30"] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv1.png" width="44"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]With Love to Customers[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]ThemeRex is a studio that aims to make their user’s experience easier and much more pleasant. You probalby won’t have a better opportunity to make sure of their competence, as well as friendliness towards their customers. Vast experience and understanding of each product’s peculiarities let ThemeRex create outstanding business solutions. item.dc:creator: trx_user
item.content:encoded: [trx_section background="#80c2e5" padding="30px 0 60px 0"] [trx_content] [trx_icon icon="icon-down-open" size="20" color="#fff" box_style="circle" align="center" style="border: 3px solid #fff;" bg_color="transparent" bottom="60"] [trx_title type="2" color="#fff" align="center" bottom="20"]Who we are[/trx_title] [trx_title type="6" color="#fff" align="center" bottom="60"]Professional team of ThemeRex studio presents this terrific Infographic Theme[/trx_title] [trx_points type="1" top="30" bottom="60"] [trx_point_item icon=" icon-camera67" color="#fff" link="#"]Fully Customizable[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item icon="icon-human50" color="#fff" link="#"]About Studio[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item icon="icon-left36" color="#fff" link="#"]Project Team[/trx_point_item] [/trx_points] [trx_more id="tab_1s"] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section id="tab_1s" background="#eff0ea"] [trx_content] [trx_tabs style="3" initial="1" tab_names="Fully Customizable|About Studio|Project Team"] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center"]FULLY Customizable[/trx_title] [trx_text size="16" align="center" bottom="60"]RockGroup is an Infographic theme that offers infinite options for creation of the unique layout for your website.[/trx_text] [trx_slider engine="swiper" pagination="no" count="3" controls="yes" titles="no" height="455" width="950" left="auto" right="auto" bottom="30"] [trx_slider_item src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/2342.png"] [trx_slider_item src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5645.png"] [trx_slider_item src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7686.png"] [/trx_slider] [trx_text size="16" align="center"]We created three popular infographic skins for business, ecology and politics. You may use these templates both for these themes and for many others, since they are quite versatile.[/trx_text] [/trx_tab] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center" bottom="60"]About STUDIO[/trx_title] [trx_columns columns="12" bottom="30"] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv1.png" width="44"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]With Love to Customers[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]ThemeRex is a studio that aims to make their user’s experience easier and much more pleasant. You probalby won’t have a better opportunity to make sure of their competence, as well as friendliness towards their customers. Vast experience and understanding of each product’s peculiarities let ThemeRex create outstanding business solutions. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv2.png" width="42"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]High Professionalism[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]Many year experience and hundreds of successful projects have made ThemeRex a professional on the web area. Within this period of time, the company has gone through a serious evolution from amateurs to leaders. We create templates for your websites that will increase your reputation and highlight your professionalism and leadership. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [/trx_columns] [trx_columns columns="12"] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv3.png" width="42"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]Serving Clients’ Goals[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]ThemeRex is doing their best to grant each owner of their themes with maximum opportunities to present their individuality, show their achievements, and establish the best contact with their audience. Using their rich experience, world’s innovations and their own web solutions the ThemeRex team creates templates that will solve your business’s tasks at maximum degree. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv4.png" width="34"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]Reliability and Prestige[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]Purchasing products from ThemeRex means entrusting your reputation to one of the best web-studios. ThemeRex company does its work with its customer in mind. That is why you are getting the best product that will perfectly suit your needs. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [/trx_columns] [/trx_tab] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center" bottom="60"]Project Team[/trx_title] [trx_team indent="yes" rounding="yes" style="3" columns="4"] [trx_team_item user="trx_user" name="Margarita Andrews" position="Web Designer" photo="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/bird_1-e1418313445363.png"] [/trx_team_item] [trx_team_item user="trx_user" name="Rosemarie Russell" align="left" position="Web Developer" photo="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/bird_2-e1418313479211.png"] [/trx_team_item] [trx_team_item user="trx_user" name="Leonard Gregory" position="Project Manager" photo="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/bird_3-e1418313510938.png"] [/trx_team_item] [/trx_team] [/trx_tab] [/trx_tabs] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#f48c75" padding="90px 0 0 0"] [trx_content] [trx_text size="90" color="#fff" weight="700" align="center" height="90" bottom="30"]6231[/trx_text] [trx_text size="24" color="#fff" weight="300" align="center" height="35" bottom="60"]...cups of coffee was consumed by our team in 2014. And yes, this figure here is for no reason. And we are presenting you TRX SKILLS WIDGET specially stylized for ROCK GROUP[/trx_text] [trx_rocks count="6" maximum="6250" color="#fff" width="700" left="auto" right="auto" bottom="60"] [trx_rocks_item level="5478" title="L1"] [trx_rocks_item level="1056" title="L2"] [trx_rocks_item level="4568" title="L3"] [trx_rocks_item level="3345" title="L4"] [trx_rocks_item level="6231" title="L5"] [trx_rocks_item level="2256" title="L6"] [/trx_rocks] [trx_more id="widget"] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section id="widget" background="#eff0ea" padding="100px 0"] [trx_content width="1100"] [trx_image url="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/234r.png" width="432" align="left" right="70"] [trx_block align="left" width="570"] [trx_title type="1" bottom="40"]Skills Widget[/trx_title] [trx_text] To display your knowledge and skills graphically, you have a specially designed widget at your disposal, such as "TRX Skills". You may choose unlimited number of skills, name them, set the level, color and one of the display styles. Vivamus vel mauris id turpis scelerisque ullamcorper. Ut non velit blandit neque aliquam finibus. Donec ornare tortor ac arcu elementum fermentum. Suspendisse rhoncus est vitae leo rutrum congue. Pellentesque nisl sapien, mollis sit amet eros in, imperdiet tempus tortor. Nulla eu lobortis sem. Mauris vitae aliquet tortor. [/trx_text] [trx_button skin="global" style="regular" size="big" top="10"]Read More[/trx_button] [/trx_block] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fcfcf7" padding="90px 0 30px 0"] [trx_content] [trx_title color="#53371c" type="2" align="center" height="35" bottom="30"]Rock is easily adaptable to any mobile device[/trx_title] [trx_text color="#53371c" align="center" size="24" weight="300" height="35" bottom="60"]The fact of prevalence of mobile devices obliges to adjust any website to peculiarities of their screens at max. We have done our best for your website based on Rock Group to blend with this trend.[/trx_text] [trx_points type="2" arrows="yes"] [trx_point_item image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/ledcinema.png" background="#d7d6cb" color="#53371c"]RETINA READY[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/macbook.png" background="#d7d6cb" color="#53371c"]TABLET FRIENDLY[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/mobile.png" background="#d7d6cb" color="#53371c"]100% RESPONSIVE[/trx_point_item] [/trx_points] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fcfcf7" padding="30px 0"] [trx_line] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fcfcf7" padding="30px 0 90px 0"] [trx_content] [trx_title color="#53371c" type="2" align="center" bottom="30"]What we do[/trx_title] [trx_title color="#53371c" type="6" align="center" bottom="60"]More information about rock group features[/trx_title] [trx_text color="#53371c" size="24" height="35" align="center" weight="300" bottom="60"]ThemeRex worked out an amazing combination of vast fucntionalilty and user’s comfort. Thanks to an amazingly user friendly TRX Framework, customers have a chance to customize their theme the way they like.[/trx_text] [trx_chart width="550" legend="no" title="100%result" bottom="80" align="center"] [trx_chart_item level="25" title="100% Responsive" color="#927150" icon="icon-mountains" icon_color="#927150"]The fact of prevalence of mobile devices obliges to adjust any website to peculiarities at maximum degree.[/trx_chart_item] [trx_chart_item level="50" title="Free Support" color="#f48c75" icon=" icon-favorite" icon_color="#f48c75"]Our Support Team is ready to become your reliable guide in the World of Rock Group. We provide free access to theme Documentation and our Ticket Sys.[/trx_chart_item] [trx_chart_item level="75" title="Shortcodes" color="#84cbc5" icon="icon-tribal" icon_color="#84cbc5"]Rock Group includes the most full set of Shortcodes, amongst which you can find those you can get only in ThemeRex products.[/trx_chart_item] [trx_chart_item level="85" title="SEO Ready" color="#868ad1" icon="icon-man" icon_color="#868ad1"]HTML5 code integrated into the theme meets the best SEO approaches. The theme supports compatibility with advanced SEO plugins.[/trx_chart_item] [/trx_chart] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#f0ede1" padding="90px 0 0 0"] [trx_content] [trx_title color="#53371c" type="2" align="center" bottom="30"]TRX framework[/trx_title] [trx_title color="#53371c" type="6" align="center" bottom="90"]COMBINATION OF VAST FUNCTIONALITY AND USER’S COMFORT![/trx_title] [trx_around bottom="-11" image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/3f4d.png" width="900" align="center"] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Unique Setting Inheritance and Override System[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Raiting \ Review Mechanism and Media Content Manager[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Shortcode Builder or Visual Composer[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Unique ThemeRex Shortcodes[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Custom Theme Options Panel[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Advanced Translation Options[/trx_around_item] [/trx_around] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fad260" padding="60px 0 0 0"] [trx_content] [trx_text align="center" color="#53371c" weight="300" height="35" size="24" bottom="30"]Common settings can be overriden for any page/category/post. For instance, you can assign your own set of parameters for each category: color scheme, sidebars, menu type, style of slider and many more.[/trx_text] [trx_more id="video_sd"] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fad260" padding="0 0 90px 0" id="video_sd"] [trx_content] [trx_video url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hZMXK3_Xe8E" autoplay="off" image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/TiffanyBug.jpg"] [trx_text align="center" color="#fff" weight="300" height="24" size="16"]TRX Framework is a result of accumulated experience of WordPress theme development and constant contact with customers. The team worked out an amazing combination of vast functionality and user’s comfort. Thanks to an incredibly user friendly TRX Framework, customers have a chance to customize their theme the way they like.[/trx_text] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#84cbc5"] item.content:encoded: [trx_section background="#a9cfd0" padding="30px 0 60px 0"] [trx_content] [trx_icon icon="icon-down-open" size="20" color="#2e3137" box_style="circle" align="center" style="border: 3px solid #2e3137;" bg_color="transparent" bottom="60"] [trx_title type="2" color="#2e3137" align="center" bottom="20"]Who we are[/trx_title] [trx_title type="6" color="#2e3137" align="center" bottom="60"]Professional team of ThemeRex studio presents this terrific Infographic Theme[/trx_title] [trx_points type="1" top="30" bottom="60"] [trx_point_item icon=" icon-camera67" color="#2e3137" link="#"]Fully Customizable[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item icon="icon-human50" color="#2e3137" link="#"]About Studio[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item icon="icon-left36" color="#2e3137" link="#"]Project Team[/trx_point_item] [/trx_points] [trx_more id="tab_1s"] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section id="tab_1s" background="#eff0ea"] [trx_content] [trx_tabs style="3" initial="1" tab_names="Fully Customizable|About Studio|Project Team"] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center"]FULLY Customizable[/trx_title] [trx_text size="16" align="center" bottom="60"]RockGroup is an Infographic theme that offers infinite options for creation of the unique layout for your website.[/trx_text] [trx_slider engine="swiper" pagination="no" count="3" controls="yes" titles="no" height="455" width="950" left="auto" right="auto" bottom="30"] [trx_slider_item src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/2342.png"] [trx_slider_item src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5645.png"] [trx_slider_item src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7686.png"] [/trx_slider] [trx_text size="16" align="center"]We created three popular infographic skins for business, ecology and politics. You may use these templates both for these themes and for many others, since they are quite versatile.[/trx_text] [/trx_tab] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center" bottom="60"]About STUDIO[/trx_title] [trx_columns columns="12" bottom="30"] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv1.png" width="44"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]With Love to Customers[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]ThemeRex is a studio that aims to make their user’s experience easier and much more pleasant. You probalby won’t have a better opportunity to make sure of their competence, as well as friendliness towards their customers. Vast experience and understanding of each product’s peculiarities let ThemeRex create outstanding business solutions. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv2.png" width="42"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]High Professionalism[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]Many year experience and hundreds of successful projects have made ThemeRex a professional on the web area. Within this period of time, the company has gone through a serious evolution from amateurs to leaders. We create templates for your websites that will increase your reputation and highlight your professionalism and leadership. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [/trx_columns] [trx_columns columns="12"] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv3.png" width="42"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]Serving Clients’ Goals[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]ThemeRex is doing their best to grant each owner of their themes with maximum opportunities to present their individuality, show their achievements, and establish the best contact with their audience. Using their rich experience, world’s innovations and their own web solutions the ThemeRex team creates templates that will solve your business’s tasks at maximum degree. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv4.png" width="34"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]Reliability and Prestige[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]Purchasing products from ThemeRex means entrusting your reputation to one of the best web-studios. ThemeRex company does its work with its customer in mind. That is why you are getting the best product that will perfectly suit your needs. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [/trx_columns] [/trx_tab] [trx_tab] [trx_title type="1" align="center" bottom="60"]Project Team[/trx_title] [trx_team indent="yes" rounding="yes" style="3" columns="4"] [trx_team_item user="trx_user" name="Margarita Andrews" position="Web Designer" photo="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/bird_1-e1418313445363.png"] [/trx_team_item] [trx_team_item user="trx_user" name="Rosemarie Russell" align="left" position="Web Developer" photo="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/bird_2-e1418313479211.png"] [/trx_team_item] [trx_team_item user="trx_user" name="Leonard Gregory" position="Project Manager" photo="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/bird_3-e1418313510938.png"] [/trx_team_item] [/trx_team] [/trx_tab] [/trx_tabs] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#e4b05a" padding="90px 0 0 0"] [trx_content] [trx_text size="90" color="#fff" weight="700" align="center" height="90" bottom="30"]6231[/trx_text] [trx_text size="24" color="#fff" weight="300" align="center" height="35" bottom="60"]...cups of coffee was consumed by our team in 2014. And yes, this figure here is for no reason. And we are presenting you TRX SKILLS WIDGET specially stylized for ROCK GROUP[/trx_text] [trx_rocks count="6" maximum="6250" color="#fff" width="700" left="auto" right="auto" bottom="60"] [trx_rocks_item level="5478" title="L1"] [trx_rocks_item level="1056" title="L2"] [trx_rocks_item level="4568" title="L3"] [trx_rocks_item level="3345" title="L4"] [trx_rocks_item level="6231" title="L5"] [trx_rocks_item level="2256" title="L6"] [/trx_rocks] [trx_more id="widget"] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section id="widget" background="#eff0ea" padding="100px 0"] [trx_content width="1100"] [trx_image url="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/234r.png" width="432" align="left" right="70"] [trx_block align="left" width="570"] [trx_title type="1" bottom="40"]Skills Widget[/trx_title] [trx_text] To display your knowledge and skills graphically, you have a specially designed widget at your disposal, such as "TRX Skills". You may choose unlimited number of skills, name them, set the level, color and one of the display styles. Vivamus vel mauris id turpis scelerisque ullamcorper. We have done our best for your website based on Rock Group to blend with this trend.[/trx_text] [trx_points type="2" arrows="yes"] [trx_point_item image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/ledcinema.png" background="#d7d6cb" color="#3b4649"]RETINA READY[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/macbook.png" background="#d7d6cb" color="#3b4649"]TABLET FRIENDLY[/trx_point_item] [trx_point_item image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/mobile.png" background="#d7d6cb" color="#3b4649"]100% RESPONSIVE[/trx_point_item] [/trx_points] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fcfcf7" padding="30px 0"] [trx_line] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#fcfcf7" padding="30px 0 90px 0"] [trx_content] [trx_title color="#3b4649" type="2" align="center" bottom="30"]What we do[/trx_title] [trx_title color="#3b4649" type="6" align="center" bottom="60"]More information about rock group features[/trx_title] [trx_text color="#3b4649" size="24" height="35" align="center" weight="300" bottom="60"]ThemeRex worked out an amazing combination of vast fucntionalilty and user’s comfort. Thanks to an incredibly user friendly TRX Framework, customers have a chance to customize their theme the way they like.[/trx_text] [trx_chart width="550" legend="no" title="100%result" bottom="80" align="center"] [trx_chart_item level="25" title="100% Responsive" color="#5c5f69" icon="icon-mountains" icon_color="#5c5f69"]The fact of prevalence of mobile devices obliges to adjust any website to peculiarities of their screens at max.[/trx_chart_item] [trx_chart_item level="50" title="Free Support" color="#cf5b47" icon=" icon-favorite" icon_color="#cf5b47"]Our Support Team is ready to become your reliable guide in the World of Rock Group. We provide free access to theme Documentation and our Ticket Sys.[/trx_chart_item] [trx_chart_item level="75" title="Shortcodes" color="#2f3237" icon="icon-tribal" icon_color="#2f3237"]Rock Group includes the most full set of Shortcodes, amongst which you can find those you can get only in ThemeRex products.[/trx_chart_item] [trx_chart_item level="85" title="SEO Ready" color="#a9cfd0" icon="icon-man" icon_color="#a9cfd0"]HTML5 code integrated into the theme meets the best SEO approaches. The theme supports compatibility with advanced SEO plugins.[/trx_chart_item] [/trx_chart] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#e5e4e4" padding="90px 0 0 0"] [trx_content] [trx_title color="#3b4649" type="2" align="center" bottom="30"]TRX framework[/trx_title] [trx_title color="#3b4649" type="6" align="center" bottom="90"]COMBINATION OF VAST FUNCTIONALITY AND USER’S COMFORT![/trx_title] [trx_around bottom="-11" image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/ee35.png" width="900" align="center"] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Unique Setting Inheritance and Override System[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Raiting \ Review Mechanism and Media Content Manager[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Shortcode Builder or Visual Composer[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Unique ThemeRex Shortcodes[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Custom Theme Options Panel[/trx_around_item] [trx_around_item link="http://themeforest.net/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&term=themerex"]Advanced Translation Options[/trx_around_item] [/trx_around] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#cf5b47" padding="60px 0 0 0"] [trx_content] [trx_text align="center" color="#fff" weight="300" height="35" size="24" bottom="30"]Common settings can be overriden for any page/category/post. For instance, you can assign your own set of parameters to each category: color scheme, sidebars, menu type, style of slider and many more.[/trx_text] [trx_more id="video_sd"] [/trx_content] [/trx_section] [trx_section background="#cf5b47" padding="0 0 90px 0" id="video_sd"] [trx_content] [trx_video url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hZMXK3_Xe8E" autoplay="off" image="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/TiffanyBug.jpg"] [trx_text align="center" color="#fff" weight="300" height="24" size="16"]TRX Framework is a result of accumulated experience of WordPress theme development and constant contact with customers. You probalby won’t have a better opportunity to make sure of their competence, as well as friendliness towards their customers. Vast experience and understanding of each product’s peculiarities let ThemeRex create outstanding business solutions. [/trx_text] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item][trx_image src="http://rockgroupwp.themerex.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/acv2.png" width="42"][/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item colspan="5"] [trx_text size="24" color="#000"]High Professionalism[/trx_text] [trx_text size="14"]Many year experience and hundreds of successful projects have made ThemeRex a professional on the web area.
